{"ID":270251, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"251\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs250.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs252.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 251<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">that is done, judgment will be administered in righteousness;<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> anarchy and confusion will be\n  destroyed, and &ldquo;nations will learn war no more.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> It is for want of this great governing principle, that\n  all this confusion has existed; &ldquo;for it is not in man that walketh, to direct his steps;&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> this we have\n  fully shown.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">If there was anything great or good in the world, it came from God.<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> The construction of the first\n  vessel was given to Noah, by revelation.<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> The design of the ark was given by God, &ldquo;a pattern of\n  heavenly things.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> The learning of the Egyptians, and their knowledge of astronomy was no doubt\n  taught them by Abraham<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> and Joseph, as their records testify, who received it from the Lord. The\n  art of working in brass,<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> silver, gold, and precious stones, was taught by revelation, in the\n  wilderness.<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> The architectural designs of the Temple at Jerusalem,<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> together with its ornaments and\n  beauty,<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> were given of God. Wisdom to govern the house of Israel was given to Solomon,<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> and the\n  Judges of Israel; and if he had always been their king, and they subject to his mandate, and obedient\n  to his laws, they would still have been a great and mighty people&mdash;the rulers of the universe, and\n  the wonder of the world.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Government Established by God<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">If Nebuchadnezzar, or Darius, or Cyrus,<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> or any other king possessed knowledge or power,<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span>\n  it was from the same source, as the Scriptures abundantly testify. If, then, God puts up one, and sets\n  down another<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span> at His pleasure,<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span> and made instruments of kings, unknown to themselves, to fulfill\n  His prophecies,<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span> how much more was He able, if man would have been subject to His mandate to\n  regulate the affairs of this world, and promote peace and happiness among the human family!<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">The Lord has at various times commenced this kind of government, and tendered His services\n  to the human family. He selected Enoch, whom He directed, and gave His law unto,<span class=\"footRef\">18<\/span> and to the\n  people who were with him; and when the world in general would not obey the commands of God,<span class=\"footRef\">19<\/span>\n  after walking with God, he translated Enoch and his church,<span class=\"footRef\">20<\/span> and the Priesthood or government of\n  heaven was taken away.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Abraham was guided in all his family affairs<span class=\"footRef\">21<\/span> by the Lord; was conversed with by angels,<span class=\"footRef\">22<\/span> and\n  by the Lord;<span class=\"footRef\">23<\/span> was told where to go, and when to stop;<span class=\"footRef\">24<\/span> and prospered exceedingly in all that<\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108712\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108712)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108712)\">John 7:24<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110088\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110088)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110088)\">2 Tim. 4:8<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111539\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111539)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111539)\">Mosiah 3:10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116838\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116838)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116838)\">Moses 6:57<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107017\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107017)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107017)\">Isa. 2:4<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107335\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107335)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107335)\">Jer. 10:23<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110349\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110349)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110349)\">James 1:17<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111471\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111471)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111471)\">Omni 1:25<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112959\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112959)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112959)\">Moro. 7:24<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"105996\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 105996)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(105996)\">Gen. 6:14-16<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110226\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110226)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110226)\">Heb. 8:5<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110239\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110239)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110239)\">Heb. 9:23<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"117000\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 117000)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(117000)\">Abr. 1:31<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"117015\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 117015)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(117015)\">Abr. 3:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106194\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106194)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106194)\">Ex. 31:1-5<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111021\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111021)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111021)\">1 Ne. 17:10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111149\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111149)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111149)\">2 Ne. 5:15-16<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106433\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106433)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106433)\">1 Kgs. 6:1-38<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106197\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106197)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106197)\">Ex. 31:6-10<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106427\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106427)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106427)\">1 Kgs. 3:9-12<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106432\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106432)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106432)\">1 Kgs. 4:29-34<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107504\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107504)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107504)\">Dan. 1:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107543\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107543)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107543)\">Dan. 6:28<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107530\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107530)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107530)\">Dan. 4:25<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107533\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107533)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107533)\">Dan. 5:21<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114154\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114154)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114154)\">D&amp;C 63:4<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109764\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109764)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109764)\">Eph. 1:9<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109333\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109333)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109333)\">Rom. 9:17<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116815\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116815)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116815)\">Moses 6:26-31<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">19. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116891\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116891)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116891)\">Moses 7:32-33<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">20. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116945\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116945)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116945)\">Moses 7:69<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">21. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116985\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116985)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116985)\">Abr. 1:16<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">22. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106042\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106042)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106042)\">Gen. 22:11<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">23. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106031\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106031)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106031)\">Gen. 18:1<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">24. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106012\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106012)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106012)\">Gen. 12:1<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}